{
  "video_id": "y7l5QHRY_AI",
  "title": "How to make a profit while making a difference | Audrey Choi",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13400.0,
      "end_time": 15560.0,
      "text": "I believe big institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15800.0,
      "end_time": 17696.0,
      "text": "have unique potential to create change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17720.0,
      "end_time": 19695.0,
      "text": "and I believe that we as individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19720.0,
      "end_time": 21160.0,
      "text": "have unique power"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21400.0,
      "end_time": 23759.0,
      "text": "to influence the direction that those institutions take."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24720.0,
      "end_time": 27550.0,
      "text": "Now, these beliefs did not come naturally to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27800.0,
      "end_time": 29656.0,
      "text": "because trusting big institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29680.0,
      "end_time": 31480.0,
      "text": "not really part of my family legacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32640.0,
      "end_time": 34736.0,
      "text": "My mother escaped North Korea"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34760.0,
      "end_time": 36616.0,
      "text": "when she was 10 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36640.0,
      "end_time": 40656.0,
      "text": "To do so, she had to elude every big institution in her life:"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40680.0,
      "end_time": 43536.0,
      "text": "repressive governments, occupying armies"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43560.0,
      "end_time": 45480.0,
      "text": "and even armed border patrols."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46720.0,
      "end_time": 50416.0,
      "text": "Later, when she decided she wanted to emigrate to the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50440.0,
      "end_time": 52495.0,
      "text": "she had to defy an entire culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52520.0,
      "end_time": 56400.0,
      "text": "that said the girls would never be the best and brightest."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56680.0,
      "end_time": 59616.0,
      "text": "Only because her name happens to sound like a boy&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59640.0,
      "end_time": 62896.0,
      "text": "was she able to finagle her way into the government immigration exam"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62920.0,
      "end_time": 64519.0,
      "text": "to come to the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65600.0,
      "end_time": 67976.0,
      "text": "Because of her bravery and passion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68000.0,
      "end_time": 70856.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had all the opportunities that she never did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70880.0,
      "end_time": 73399.0,
      "text": "and that has made my story so different."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74800.0,
      "end_time": 76456.0,
      "text": "Instead of running away from big institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76480.0,
      "end_time": 78296.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve actually run toward them."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78320.0,
      "end_time": 80576.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had the chance over the course of my career"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80600.0,
      "end_time": 82416.0,
      "text": "to work for The Wall Street Journal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82440.0,
      "end_time": 83655.0,
      "text": "the White House"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83680.0,
      "end_time": 86656.0,
      "text": "and now one of the largest financial institutions in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86680.0,
      "end_time": 88816.0,
      "text": "where I lead sustainable investing."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88840.0,
      "end_time": 91256.0,
      "text": "Now, these institutions are like tankers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91280.0,
      "end_time": 92696.0,
      "text": "and working inside of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 92720.0,
      "end_time": 96336.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve come to appreciate what large wakes they can leave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96360.0,
      "end_time": 97656.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve become convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 97680.0,
      "end_time": 100416.0,
      "text": "that the institution of the global capital markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100440.0,
      "end_time": 105336.0,
      "text": "the nearly 290 trillion dollars of stocks and bonds in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105360.0,
      "end_time": 108216.0,
      "text": "that that may be one of our most powerful forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108240.0,
      "end_time": 110815.0,
      "text": "for positive social change at our disposal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 110840.0,
      "end_time": 112800.0,
      "text": "if we ask it to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 112920.0,
      "end_time": 114776.0,
      "text": "Now, I know some of you are thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114800.0,
      "end_time": 117295.0,
      "text": "global capital markets, positive social change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117320.0,
      "end_time": 121136.0,
      "text": "not usually in the same sentence or even the same paragraph."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121160.0,
      "end_time": 123496.0,
      "text": "I think many people think of the capital markets"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123520.0,
      "end_time": 124816.0,
      "text": "kind of like an ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124840.0,
      "end_time": 128656.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a vast, impersonal, uncaring force of nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128680.0,
      "end_time": 131336.0,
      "text": "that is not affected by our wishes or desires."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 131360.0,
      "end_time": 133696.0,
      "text": "So the best that our little savings accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133720.0,
      "end_time": 135416.0,
      "text": "or retirement accounts can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135440.0,
      "end_time": 138160.0,
      "text": "is to try to catch some waves in the good cycles"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 138400.0,
      "end_time": 140801.0,
      "text": "and hope that we don&#39;t get inundated in the turbulent ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 140826.0,
      "end_time": 145550.0,
      "text": "but certainly our decisions on how to steer our little retirement accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 145800.0,
      "end_time": 146576.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t affect the tides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 146600.0,
      "end_time": 150000.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t change the shape or size or direction of the waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151800.0,
      "end_time": 153160.0,
      "text": "But why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153400.0,
      "end_time": 156376.0,
      "text": "Because actually, one third of this ocean of capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156400.0,
      "end_time": 160160.0,
      "text": "actually belongs to individuals like us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160400.0,
      "end_time": 162960.0,
      "text": "and most of the rest of the capital markets"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 162120.0,
      "end_time": 165336.0,
      "text": "is controlled by the institutions that get their power and authority"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 165360.0,
      "end_time": 167136.0,
      "text": "and their capital from us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 167160.0,
      "end_time": 171296.0,
      "text": "as members, participants, beneficiaries, shareholders or citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 171320.0,
      "end_time": 174160.0,
      "text": "So if we are the ultimate owners of the capital markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175240.0,
      "end_time": 177360.0,
      "text": "why aren&#39;t we able to make our voices heard?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178360.0,
      "end_time": 179920.0,
      "text": "Why can&#39;t we make some waves?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 180960.0,
      "end_time": 182856.0,
      "text": "So let me ask you a different question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 182880.0,
      "end_time": 185960.0,
      "text": "did any of you buy fair trade coffee"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 185120.0,
      "end_time": 187776.0,
      "text": "the last time you were at a supermarket or at Starbucks?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 187800.0,
      "end_time": 190216.0,
      "text": "OK. Do any of you go to the restaurant"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 190240.0,
      "end_time": 192896.0,
      "text": "and order the sustainably farmed trout"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 192920.0,
      "end_time": 195456.0,
      "text": "instead of the miso-glazed Chilean sea bass"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 195480.0,
      "end_time": 197200.0,
      "text": "that you really wish you could have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 197960.0,
      "end_time": 200840.0,
      "text": "Do any of you drive hybrid cars or even electric cars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 201440.0,
      "end_time": 203536.0,
      "text": "So why do we do these things?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 203560.0,
      "end_time": 207416.0,
      "text": "Right? One electric car doesn&#39;t amount to much in a fleet of 1.2 billion"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 207440.0,
      "end_time": 208920.0,
      "text": "combustion engine vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 209760.0,
      "end_time": 212440.0,
      "text": "One fish is just one fish in the sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 213160.0,
      "end_time": 215335.0,
      "text": "And one cup of coffee"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 215360.0,
      "end_time": 217920.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t amount to a hill of beans in this crazy world."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 219400.0,
      "end_time": 221936.0,
      "text": "But we do these things because we believe they matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 221960.0,
      "end_time": 223216.0,
      "text": "that our actions add up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 223240.0,
      "end_time": 225136.0,
      "text": "that our choices might influence others"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 225160.0,
      "end_time": 227320.0,
      "text": "and collectively, what an impact we can have."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 228440.0,
      "end_time": 231856.0,
      "text": "So, in my bag I have a coffee mug that I bought a couple of years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 231880.0,
      "end_time": 234816.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a reusable mug. It has all these things printed on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 234840.0,
      "end_time": 237936.0,
      "text": "Look at some of the things that are on it, that it says."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 237960.0,
      "end_time": 240496.0,
      "text": "\"This one cup can be used again and again.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 240520.0,
      "end_time": 244376.0,
      "text": "\"This one cup may inspire others to use one too.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 244400.0,
      "end_time": 246696.0,
      "text": "\"This one cup helps save the planet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 246720.0,
      "end_time": 249176.0,
      "text": "I had no idea this plastic cup was so powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 249200.0,
      "end_time": 250296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 250320.0,
      "end_time": 252215.0,
      "text": "So why do we think that our choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 252240.0,
      "end_time": 256550.0,
      "text": "of a four dollar shade-grown fair trade artisanal cup of coffee"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 256790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258255.00000000003,
      "text": "in a reusable mug matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 258279.0,
      "end_time": 261410.0,
      "text": "but what we do with 4,000 dollars in our investment account"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 261649.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262465.0,
      "text": "for our IRA doesn&#39;t?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 263800.0,
      "end_time": 266896.0,
      "text": "Why can&#39;t we tell the supermarket and the capital markets"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 266920.0,
      "end_time": 268336.0,
      "text": "that we care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 268360.0,
      "end_time": 270616.0,
      "text": "that we care about fair labor standards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 270640.0,
      "end_time": 272976.0,
      "text": "that we care about sustainable production methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 273000.0,
      "end_time": 274856.0,
      "text": "and about healthy communities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 274880.0,
      "end_time": 277896.0,
      "text": "Why aren&#39;t we voting with our investment dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 277920.0,
      "end_time": 279560.0,
      "text": "but we would vote with our lattes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 280520.0,
      "end_time": 283736.0,
      "text": "So I think it has something to do with the myths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 283760.0,
      "end_time": 286976.0,
      "text": "the fables that we all carry around in our collective consciousness."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 287000.0,
      "end_time": 290576.0,
      "text": "Do you remember the Grimm&#39;s fairy tale about the magic porridge pot?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 290600.0,
      "end_time": 292976.0,
      "text": "If you said to the pot, \"Boil, little pot, boil,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 293000.0,
      "end_time": 295296.0,
      "text": "it would fill up with sweet porridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 295320.0,
      "end_time": 297416.0,
      "text": "And if you said, \"Stop, little pot, stop,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 297440.0,
      "end_time": 298640.0,
      "text": "it would stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 299440.0,
      "end_time": 302616.0,
      "text": "But if you got the words wrong, it wouldn&#39;t listen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 302640.0,
      "end_time": 304400.0,
      "text": "and things could go terribly awry."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 305640.0,
      "end_time": 307376.0,
      "text": "So I think when it comes to markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 307400.0,
      "end_time": 309895.0,
      "text": "we have a little bit of a similar fable in our heads."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 309920.0,
      "end_time": 312256.0,
      "text": "We believe that the markets is this magic pot"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 312280.0,
      "end_time": 314135.0,
      "text": "that obeys only one command:"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 314160.0,
      "end_time": 316200.0,
      "text": "make more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 316920.0,
      "end_time": 319816.0,
      "text": "Only those words said exactly that way"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 319840.0,
      "end_time": 321679.0,
      "text": "will make the pot fill up with gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 322640.0,
      "end_time": 325976.0,
      "text": "Add in some extra words like \"protect the environment,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 326000.0,
      "end_time": 327640.0,
      "text": "the spell might not work."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 328400.0,
      "end_time": 331159.0,
      "text": "Put in the wrong words like \"promote social justice,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 332560.0,
      "end_time": 334576.0,
      "text": "and you might see your gold coins shrink"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 334600.0,
      "end_time": 337440.0,
      "text": "or even vanish entirely, according to this fable."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 338440.0,
      "end_time": 341216.0,
      "text": "So we asked people, what do you really think?"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 341240.0,
      "end_time": 345456.0,
      "text": "And we actually went out and polled a thousand individual investors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 345480.0,
      "end_time": 347496.0,
      "text": "and we found something fascinating."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 347520.0,
      "end_time": 349150.0,
      "text": "Overwhelmingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 349400.0,
      "end_time": 352656.0,
      "text": "people wanted to add those extra words into the formula."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 352680.0,
      "end_time": 355736.0,
      "text": "71 percent of people said yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 355760.0,
      "end_time": 358336.0,
      "text": "they were interested in sustainable investing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 358360.0,
      "end_time": 361296.0,
      "text": "which we define as taking the best in class investment process"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 361320.0,
      "end_time": 363560.0,
      "text": "that you already have traditionally"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 363800.0,
      "end_time": 365135.0,
      "text": "and adding in the extra information you get"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 365160.0,
      "end_time": 368416.0,
      "text": "when you think about the environment and society and good governance."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 368440.0,
      "end_time": 370176.0,
      "text": "71 percent wanted that."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 370200.0,
      "end_time": 373856.0,
      "text": "72 percent said that they believe that companies who did that"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 373880.0,
      "end_time": 375695.0,
      "text": "would actually do better financially."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 375720.0,
      "end_time": 379376.0,
      "text": "So people really do believe that you can do well by doing good."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 379400.0,
      "end_time": 380816.0,
      "text": "But here was the weird thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 380840.0,
      "end_time": 382376.0,
      "text": "54 percent of the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 382400.0,
      "end_time": 386575.0,
      "text": "still said if they put their money in those kinds of stocks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 386600.0,
      "end_time": 388720.0,
      "text": "they thought that they would make less money."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 389880.0,
      "end_time": 391496.0,
      "text": "So is it true?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 391520.0,
      "end_time": 395296.0,
      "text": "Do you get less sweet porridge if you invest in shade-grown coffee"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 395320.0,
      "end_time": 396560.0,
      "text": "instead of drinking it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 397840.0,
      "end_time": 401150.0,
      "text": "Well, you know, the investors in companies like Burt&#39;s Bees"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 401400.0,
      "end_time": 402816.0,
      "text": "or Ben & Jerry&#39;s wouldn&#39;t say so."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 402840.0,
      "end_time": 406816.0,
      "text": "Right? Both of those started out as small, socially conscious companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 406840.0,
      "end_time": 409976.0,
      "text": "that ended up becoming so popular with consumers"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 410000.0,
      "end_time": 413560.0,
      "text": "that the giants Unilever and Clorox bought them"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 413800.0,
      "end_time": 415240.0,
      "text": "for hundreds of millions of dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 415880.0,
      "end_time": 417800.0,
      "text": "each."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 417840.0,
      "end_time": 419376.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the important thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 419400.0,
      "end_time": 420736.0,
      "text": "Those corporations realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 420760.0,
      "end_time": 423695.0,
      "text": "that if they wanted to protect the value of their investments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 423720.0,
      "end_time": 426216.0,
      "text": "they had to preserve that socially conscious mission."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 426240.0,
      "end_time": 428456.0,
      "text": "If they didn&#39;t keep adding in those extra words"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 428480.0,
      "end_time": 430896.0,
      "text": "of environmentally friendly and socially conscious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 430920.0,
      "end_time": 433000.0,
      "text": "those brands wouldn&#39;t make more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 434440.0,
      "end_time": 437776.0,
      "text": "But maybe this is just the exception the proves the rule, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 437800.0,
      "end_time": 440336.0,
      "text": "The serious companies that fund our economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 440360.0,
      "end_time": 443656.0,
      "text": "and that fund our retirements and that really make the world go round,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 443680.0,
      "end_time": 446120.0,
      "text": "they need to stick to making more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 446960.0,
      "end_time": 449656.0,
      "text": "So, Harvard Business School actually researched this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 449680.0,
      "end_time": 451442.0,
      "text": "and they found something fascinating."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 451466.0,
      "end_time": 454960.0,
      "text": "If you had invested a dollar 20 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 454120.0,
      "end_time": 455776.0,
      "text": "in a portfolio of companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 455800.0,
      "end_time": 458160.0,
      "text": "that focused narrowly on making more money"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 458400.0,
      "end_time": 459976.0,
      "text": "quarter by quarter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 460000.0,
      "end_time": 461416.0,
      "text": "that one dollar"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 461440.0,
      "end_time": 465296.0,
      "text": "would have grown to 14 dollars and 46 cents."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 465320.0,
      "end_time": 467575.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not bad until you consider"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 467600.0,
      "end_time": 470616.0,
      "text": "that if instead you&#39;d invested that same dollar"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 470640.0,
      "end_time": 472296.0,
      "text": "in a portfolio of companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 472320.0,
      "end_time": 474130.0,
      "text": "that focused on growing their business"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 474154.0,
      "end_time": 477394.0,
      "text": "and on the most important environmental and social issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 478400.0,
      "end_time": 480216.0,
      "text": "that one dollar would have grown"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 480240.0,
      "end_time": 483680.0,
      "text": "to 28 dollars and 36 cents."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 484240.0,
      "end_time": 487136.0,
      "text": "almost twice as much sweet porridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 487160.0,
      "end_time": 490136.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s be clear, they didn&#39;t make that outperformance"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 490160.0,
      "end_time": 493560.0,
      "text": "by giving away money to seem like a nice corporate citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 493800.0,
      "end_time": 496296.0,
      "text": "They did it by focusing on the things that matter to their business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 496320.0,
      "end_time": 498736.0,
      "text": "like wasting less energy and water"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 498760.0,
      "end_time": 500536.0,
      "text": "in their manufacturing processes;"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 500560.0,
      "end_time": 503936.0,
      "text": "like making sure the CEO contracts had the CEOs incentivized"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 503960.0,
      "end_time": 507416.0,
      "text": "for the long-term results of the company and the communities they served,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 507440.0,
      "end_time": 508816.0,
      "text": "not just quarterly results;"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 508840.0,
      "end_time": 511135.0,
      "text": "or building a first class culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 511160.0,
      "end_time": 513496.0,
      "text": "that would have higher employee loyalty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 513520.0,
      "end_time": 515480.0,
      "text": "retention and productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 516480.0,
      "end_time": 517736.0,
      "text": "Now, Harvard&#39;s not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 517760.0,
      "end_time": 521775.0,
      "text": "Oxford also did a research study where they examined 120 different studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 521799.0,
      "end_time": 525256.0,
      "text": "looking at the effect of sustainability and economic results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 525280.0,
      "end_time": 528550.0,
      "text": "and they found time and time and time again"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 528800.0,
      "end_time": 531936.0,
      "text": "that the companies that cared about these kinds of important things"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 531960.0,
      "end_time": 534000.0,
      "text": "actually had better operational efficiency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 534600.0,
      "end_time": 536416.0,
      "text": "lower cost of capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 536440.0,
      "end_time": 538680.0,
      "text": "and better performance in their stock price."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 539320.0,
      "end_time": 540856.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s Al Gore."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 540880.0,
      "end_time": 543816.0,
      "text": "So 20 years ago, when I worked for Al Gore in the White House,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 543840.0,
      "end_time": 547296.0,
      "text": "he was one of the early pioneers pleading with businesses and governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 547320.0,
      "end_time": 550160.0,
      "text": "to pay attention to the challenges of climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 550400.0,
      "end_time": 553880.0,
      "text": "Post-White House, he opened an investment firm called Generation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 553112.0,
      "end_time": 556376.0,
      "text": "where he baked environmental sustainability and other things"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 556400.0,
      "end_time": 558280.0,
      "text": "right into the core investment process."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 558840.0,
      "end_time": 562496.0,
      "text": "And at the time there was a good bit of skepticism about his views."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 562520.0,
      "end_time": 566256.0,
      "text": "Ten years later, his track record is one more proof point"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 566280.0,
      "end_time": 569976.0,
      "text": "that sustainable investing done right can be sound investing."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 570000.0,
      "end_time": 571856.0,
      "text": "Far from making less sweet porridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 571880.0,
      "end_time": 574256.0,
      "text": "because he added sustainability into the mix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 574280.0,
      "end_time": 576959.0,
      "text": "he actually significantly outperformed the benchmark."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 577560.0,
      "end_time": 579950.0,
      "text": "Now, sustainable investing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 579120.0,
      "end_time": 582000.0,
      "text": "the good news is it doesn&#39;t require a magic spell"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 582920.0,
      "end_time": 586960.0,
      "text": "and it doesn&#39;t require some investment secret,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 586120.0,
      "end_time": 587696.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s not just for the elite."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 587720.0,
      "end_time": 591216.0,
      "text": "It is not just about private equity for billionaires."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 591240.0,
      "end_time": 594193.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just groovy-sounding investments like clean technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 594217.0,
      "end_time": 595913.0,
      "text": "or microfinance in emerging markets"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 595937.0,
      "end_time": 598160.0,
      "text": "or artisanal bakeries in Brooklyn."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 599000.0,
      "end_time": 602160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about stocks and bonds and Fortune 500 companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 602400.0,
      "end_time": 603256.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about mutual funds."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 603280.0,
      "end_time": 604736.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about all the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 604760.0,
      "end_time": 606920.0,
      "text": "we already see in the market today."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 607520.0,
      "end_time": 609496.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s why I&#39;m convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 609520.0,
      "end_time": 611656.0,
      "text": "that we collectively have the power"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 611680.0,
      "end_time": 614760.0,
      "text": "to make sustainable investing the new normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 615560.0,
      "end_time": 619776.0,
      "text": "First, the proof points are coming out all the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 619800.0,
      "end_time": 621815.0,
      "text": "that sustainable investing done right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 621840.0,
      "end_time": 625560.0,
      "text": "preserving all the same good principles of investing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 625800.0,
      "end_time": 627400.0,
      "text": "the traditional sphere, can pay."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 627520.0,
      "end_time": 629336.0,
      "text": "It makes sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 629360.0,
      "end_time": 630776.0,
      "text": "Secondly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 630800.0,
      "end_time": 632935.0,
      "text": "the biggest obstacle standing in our way"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 632960.0,
      "end_time": 635000.0,
      "text": "may actually just be in our heads."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 635520.0,
      "end_time": 637576.0,
      "text": "We just need to let go of that myth"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 637600.0,
      "end_time": 641856.0,
      "text": "that if you add your values into your investment thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 641880.0,
      "end_time": 643496.0,
      "text": "that you get less sweet porridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 643520.0,
      "end_time": 645175.0,
      "text": "And once you get rid of the fable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 645200.0,
      "end_time": 648656.0,
      "text": "you can actually start appreciating those facts we&#39;ve been talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 648680.0,
      "end_time": 650656.0,
      "text": "And third, the future is already here."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 650680.0,
      "end_time": 653656.0,
      "text": "Sustainable investment today is a 20 trillion dollar market"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 653680.0,
      "end_time": 657550.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s the fastest-growing segment of the investment industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 657800.0,
      "end_time": 660296.0,
      "text": "In the United States, it has grown enormously, as you can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 660320.0,
      "end_time": 663160.0,
      "text": "It now represents one out of every six dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 663400.0,
      "end_time": 665439.0,
      "text": "under professional management in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 666400.0,
      "end_time": 667720.0,
      "text": "So what are we waiting for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 669160.0,
      "end_time": 672493.0,
      "text": "For me, it goes back to the inspiration that I received from my mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 673240.0,
      "end_time": 674776.0,
      "text": "She knew that she wanted a life"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 674800.0,
      "end_time": 677439.0,
      "text": "where she would have the freedom to make her own choices"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 678280.0,
      "end_time": 681496.0,
      "text": "and to have her voice heard and write her own story."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 681520.0,
      "end_time": 683976.0,
      "text": "She was passionate about that goal"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 684000.0,
      "end_time": 687616.0,
      "text": "and she was clear that she would let no army, no obstacle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 687640.0,
      "end_time": 690160.0,
      "text": "no big institution stand in her way."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 691400.0,
      "end_time": 692896.0,
      "text": "She made it to the States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 692920.0,
      "end_time": 694656.0,
      "text": "and she became a teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 694680.0,
      "end_time": 696376.0,
      "text": "an award-winning author"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 696400.0,
      "end_time": 697656.0,
      "text": "and a mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 697680.0,
      "end_time": 700376.0,
      "text": "and ended up sending her daughters to Harvard."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 700400.0,
      "end_time": 703496.0,
      "text": "And these days, you can tell that she is amply comfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 703520.0,
      "end_time": 707576.0,
      "text": "holding court in the most powerful institutions in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 707600.0,
      "end_time": 709496.0,
      "text": "It seems almost too prophetic"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 709520.0,
      "end_time": 711816.0,
      "text": "that her name in Korean means"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 711840.0,
      "end_time": 713120.0,
      "text": "\"passionate clarity.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 714280.0,
      "end_time": 715935.0,
      "text": "Passionate clarity:"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 715960.0,
      "end_time": 718736.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s what I think we need to drive change."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 718760.0,
      "end_time": 722960.0,
      "text": "Passion about the change we want to see in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 722120.0,
      "end_time": 725760.0,
      "text": "and clarity that we are able to help chart the course."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 726520.0,
      "end_time": 729496.0,
      "text": "We have more opportunity today than ever before"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 729520.0,
      "end_time": 730760.0,
      "text": "to make choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 731160.0,
      "end_time": 735400.0,
      "text": "We have more power than ever before to make our voices heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 736800.0,
      "end_time": 739120.0,
      "text": "So change your perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 740240.0,
      "end_time": 741936.0,
      "text": "Vote with your small change."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 741960.0,
      "end_time": 744840.0,
      "text": "Invest in the change you want to see in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
